data.description: This 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms well-maintained townhome features an open floor plan with an updated kitchen with granite countertops and newer stainless steel appliances. Vinyl flooring covers the first floor, while the second floor boasts newer laminate flooring. Screened-in patio with tile flooring. The spacious master bedroom includes a walk-in closet, and the home comes equipped with a full-size washer/dryer and accordion shutters throughout. Just a few steps from the community pool. Roof is less than 1 year old. Low HOA fee that includes basic cable TV, lawn care, sprinkler maintenance, swimming pool, exterior painting and roof. It is zoned for rated ''A'' schools. This property is an excellent opportunity for a first home buyer or future investment. VA and FHA approved community.
